'''查德威克氏徵象'''是[[懷孕|懷孕]]的早期[[醫學徵象|醫學徵象]]之一，是指因{{le|血流|Blood flow}}量增加，[[陰道|陰道]]、[[陰唇|陰唇]]及[[子宮頸|子宮頸]]呈藍紫色的情形，最早會在受精後六至八週出現<ref>註：有時會更早，[http://www.pregnancytoday.com/glossary/232-Chadwick%27s+Sign/ pregnancytoday.com] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090722151817/http://www.pregnancytoday.com/glossary/232-Chadwick%27s+Sign/ |date=2009-07-22 }}</ref>

查德威克氏徵象最早是在1836年由法國醫生[[艾蒂安·约瑟夫·雅克曼|艾蒂安·约瑟夫·雅克曼]]（{{lang|fr|Étienne Joseph Jacquemin}}，1796-1872）發現<ref name="pmid4925842">{{Cite journal|first = James E.|last = Gleichert|title = Étienne Joseph Jacquemin, Discoverer of 'Chadwick's Sign'|url = https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-the-history-of-medicine-and-allied-sciences_1971-01_26_1/page/75|journal = Journal of the History of Medicine and Allied Sciences|volume = 26|issue = 1|pages = 75–80|year = 1971|pmid = 4925842|doi = 10.1093/jhmas/XXVI.1.75}}</ref> ，此徵象得名自{{le|詹姆斯·瑞德·查德威克|James Read Chadwick}}，他在一篇論文中提及此徵象，認為雅克曼是第一個發現此徵象的人，查德威克在1886年在美國婦產科學會前讀了此論文，並在第二年出版<ref name="pmid4925842">{{Cite journal|first = James E.|last = Gleichert|title = Étienne Joseph Jacquemin, Discoverer of 'Chadwick's Sign'|url = https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-the-history-of-medicine-and-allied-sciences_1971-01_26_1/page/75|journal = Journal of the History of Medicine and Allied Sciences|volume = 26|issue = 1|pages = 75–80|year = 1971|pmid = 4925842|doi = 10.1093/jhmas/XXVI.1.75}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|first = James Reed|last = Chadwick|title = The value of the bluish discoloration of the vaginal entrance as a sign of pregnancy|journal = Transactions of the American Gynecological Society|year = 1887|pages = 399–418|issue = 11}}</ref>。

